title: Swansea City transfer rumours Swans linked with Brentford midfielder Alan Judge
text:
Swansea City transfer rumours: Swans linked with Brentford midfielder Alan Judge 
Wales Online Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Swansea City are reportedly eyeing Brentford star Alan Judge. Reports claim the Swans and Bournemouth have both shown an interest in the 26-year-old midfielder who joined from Blackburn in 2014. Swansea scouts are said to have watched him in recent weeks, with reports suggesting he could potentially become a January transfer target. The Swans' wide scouting network often sees them linked with players who they watch, and it remains to be seen whether anything concrete will come of it.
